name: "Quiffy" - NICOPET #0024
description:
Hello there my name is Quiffy! I was born on 7/10/2021 to Nico Pets Litter #5 INFO: Nico Pets are a collection of randomly generated 3D animated wiggly wobbly buddies released exclusively on the Tezos blockchain. |||||| DEV LOG:
7-10-2021 Hey everyone, it's finally the weekend here, which means one thing for NicoPets, WEEKEND RARITIES. In today's litter there will be not one, BUT TWO weekend rarities dropped for your enjoyment. These NicoPets come with added traits, colors, and features that make them stand out amongst the crowd! Look out for NicoPet Weekend Rarities on Saturdays from now on.   
7-9-2021 Another great day of selling NicoPets! list is updated on nicodaunt.com/nicopets...added more particle effects, different faces/eyes and new/ rare features coming in today's litter! Thanks to everyone who's joined in so far! dm me @nicodaunt if you want to bring your Kalamint NicoPet into HicEtNunc, transfers are free for the next week!||| 7-8-2021 Delightfully stoked on the success of the first two litters of NicoPets. The devlog will only ever run three entries deep as to keep from clogging the NFT's description. I've recently claimed the domain nicopets.nft, .nfts are still not functional yet, but that will be the place where all nicopet info and archived devlogs will go once its up! For now, check out nicodaunt.com/nicopets for a running list of available nicopets! ||| As for now there will be 3-5 Nico Pets born daily, look out for new litters on hicetnunc DM me on Instagram or Twitter for more info @nicodaunt
